Google has revealed its best apps and games from the Play Store for 2019. The title of Best App went to Ablo, a social networking app that allows users from around the world to connect and send messages which are automatically translated into the receiver’s language. First-person shooter Call of Duty: Mobile was chosen as the Best Game of 2019. In addition to this year’s selections from Google, the company held a special vote to let users choose their favourite app, game, movie, and book. The Users’ Choice Best App went to Glitch Video Effects, a video-editing app that lets users add more than 100 effects to their videos. Call of Duty: Mobile was also voted as Users’ Choice Best Game. For Best Movie, most participants voted for Avengers: Endgame, while Scary Stories to Tell in the Dark was chosen as the Best Book. Below is the full list of Google’s Best apps and games of 2019. <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-331284" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Ablo.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="318" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Ablo.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Ablo-600x298.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-331292" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Appy-Weather-app.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="388" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Appy-Weather-app.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Appy-Weather-app-600x364.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-331290" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Peleton-640x430.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/